title: Mets pour it on Dodgers, send NLCS back to L.A.
description: Pete Alonso golfed an early three-run homer and the Mets hammered an ineffective Jack Flaherty, extending the NLCS with a 12-6 victory over the Dodgers in Game 5 on Friday.

title: Verstappen strikes back with US GP Sprint pole as Norris bemoans 'shocking' lap
description: Max Verstappen will start from the head of a Formula 1 grid for the first time in almost four months on Saturday after he took pole position for the Sprint at the United States Grand Prix, with title rival Lando Norris only fourth.

title: Sainz leads Ferrari one-two ahead of Sprint Qualifying in Austin
description: Carlos Sainz pipped Charles Leclerc in a Ferrari one-two ahead of Sprint Qualifying for the United States Grand Prix as title contenders Max Verstappen and Lando Norris were closely matched in practice.
